title: Kylie Jenner’s Business Attire Is Anything But Office Appropriate
text:
Kylie Jenner’s Business Attire Is Anything But Office Appropriate Celebuzz | February 22, 2017 - 1:02 pm Share < br />this article: CREDIT: Instagram/Kylie Jenner 
Kylie Jenner may be a businesswoman, but don’t expect her to rock a pantsuit any time soon. 
The 19-year-old was recently spotted attending a business meeting clad in, well, what you would wear for bae in bed. Per TMZ : 
Kylie Jenner’s business attire will get any exec to bend over backwards … and every other direction she wants. 
Paps got Kylie leaving a meeting in Bev Hills, where she looked smokin’ hot in a low cut dress/lingerie — with strappy stilettos to complete the ensemble … and the biz deal, we’re sure.
